 下面是与css3的颜色，文字，背景相关的效果展示 <br>
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    <style type="text/css">
        #linear-gradient{
        width: 600px;height: 150px;line-height: 150px;text-align:center;color: #000;font-size:24px;
        background-image:linear-gradient(to left, red, orange,yellow,green,blue,indigo,violet);font-family: "MOOC Font";} 
    </style>
    <div id="linear-gradient">右下角向左上角的线性渐变背景linear-gradient</div><br>

    <style type="text/css">
        #ellipsis{text-overflow:ellipsis; overflow:hidden; white-space:nowrap; width:500px; background:#ccc;}
    </style>
    <!-- text-overflow只是用来说明文字溢出时用什么方式显示，要实现溢出时产生省略号的效果，
    还须定义强制文本在一行内显示（white-space:nowrap）及溢出内容为隐藏（overflow:hidden），
    只有这样才能实现溢出文本显示省略号的效果
    {text-overflow:ellipsis; overflow:hidden; white-space:nowrap;} -->
    <div id="ellipsis">text-overflow:ellipsis; overflow:hidden; white-space:nowrap;省略号</div><br>

    <style type="text/css">
        @font-face{
            font-family: "MOOC Font";
            src: url("http://www.imooc.com/Amaranth-BoldItalic.otf");}
        #font-face{width: 340px;padding: 30px;color: #566F89;background: #000;font-size:58px;font-family: "MOOC Font";}
    </style>
    <div id="font-face">@font-face</div><br>

    <style>
        #text-shadow{width: 400px;padding: 30px;font: bold 55px/100% "微软雅黑";background: #C5DFF8;
                text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px red;}
    </style>
    <div id="text-shadow">text-shadow</div><br>
    
    <style>
        #background-origin {
            width:220px; border:20px dashed #000; padding:20px; font-weight:bold; color:#000; 
            background:#ccc url(http://static.mukewang.com/static/img/logo_index.png) no-repeat; 
            position: relative;
            background-origin: content-box;}
        #background-origin span { position: absolute; left:0; top:0;}
        .content {height:80px; border:1px solid blue;}
    </style>
    background-origin: border-box | padding-box | content-box;
    <div id="background-origin"><span>padding</span>
        <div class="content">content</div>
    </div><br>
    
    <style>
        #background-clip {
            width:220px;border:20px dashed #000; padding:20px; font-weight:bold; color:#000; 
            background:#ccc url(http://static.mukewang.com/static/img/logo_index.png) no-repeat; 
            background-origin: border-box;
            background-clip: ?;
            position: relative;
        }
        #background-clip span {position: absolute; left:0; top:0;}
    </style>
    background-clip:border-box | padding-box | content-box | no-clip;
    <div id="background-clip"><span>padding</span>
        <div class="content">content</div>
    </div>

